== 开发和制作 ==
在2013年7月30日的[[电视评论协会|电视评论协会]]2013夏季媒体见面会上[[CW电视网|CW电视网]]首次表示将计划让[[绿箭侠_(电视剧)|绿箭侠]]引导一部新剧，新剧描写第二代[[闪电侠|闪电侠]][[巴里·艾倫|巴里·艾倫]]的故事<ref name="DeadlineAnnouncement" />，并计划在绿箭侠第二季第八、九以及二十集登场，而第二十集将作为后门试播集<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://tvfantasy.net/2013/08/01/2013-tca-summer-cw/ |title=电视评论协会2013夏季媒体见面会专题报道：CW |access-date=2014-06-19 |archive-date=2020-03-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200330115857/http://tvfantasy.net/2013/08/01/2013-tca-summer-cw/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/07/tca-greg-berlanti-talks-cws-the-flash/ |title=The Flash Will Be Introduced In 3 ‘Arrow’ Episodes, Will Start Off As “Ordinary Man” |access-date=2014-06-19 |archive-date=2014-08-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140803055314/http://www.deadline.com/2013/07/tca-greg-berlanti-talks-cws-the-flash/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="THRJuly2013" />。

然而在2013年11月18日[[CW电视网|CW电视网]]决定取消拍摄后门试播集的方法，而是和大部分新剧一样单独拍摄[[电视试播|试映集]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://tvfantasy.net/2013/11/20/shows-in-development-2013-11-19/ |title=11月19日新剧开发及剧集变动消息 |access-date=2014-06-20 |archive-date=2020-05-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200519214555/http://tvfantasy.net/2013/11/20/shows-in-development-2013-11-19/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.deadline.com/2013/11/cws-the-flash-to-do-standalone-pilot-instead-of-arrow-backdoor-pilot-episode/ |title=CW’s ‘The Flash’ To Do Stand-Alone Pilot Instead Of ‘Arrow’ Backdoor Pilot Episode |access-date=2014-06-19 |archive-date=2013-11-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131119211413/http://www.deadline.com/2013/11/cws-the-flash-to-do-standalone-pilot-instead-of-arrow-backdoor-pilot-episode/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2014年5月8日[[CW电视网|CW电视网]]正式预定本剧<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://tvfantasy.net/2014/05/09/breaking-news-abc-nbc-cw-cbs-usa-news-before-upfronts/ |title=快讯：ABC、NBC、CW、CBS和USA提前公布一批2014-2015播出季信息 |access-date=2014-06-20 |archive-date=2020-03-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200330115911/http://tvfantasy.net/2014/05/09/breaking-news-abc-nbc-cw-cbs-usa-news-before-upfronts/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2014/05/08/development-update-thursday-may-8-the-cw-picks-up-quartet-of-new-dramas-120315/10856/ |title=Development Update: Thursday, May 8 - The CW Picks Up Quartet of New Dramas |access-date=2014-06-20 |archive-date=2019-07-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190713020351/http://www.thefutoncritic.com/news/2014/05/08/development-update-thursday-may-8-the-cw-picks-up-quartet-of-new-dramas-120315/10856/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

